{"tid":762754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]老豆視網膜穿窿(有個LON) 好驚佢盲","createTime":"2018-07-31T14:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T17:09:03.000Z","uid":126911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3dd0eb3e2b438e452f32245fc43f94f27aeccc","tid":762754,"uid":126911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"想問下有冇康復 OR 受影響既巴絲 解答到...<br />\n<br />\n我老豆係今個月內脫左三次...都係左眼... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次都係一朦就去睇醫生加即時做激光手術....<br />\n老豆本身兩隻眼都有近視..一隻7XX(左,右就3-4XX... 已經冇戴CON 1~2年...<br />\n好想知點解一直會穿窿.. 穿既第一次之後已經冇做任何負重用力既野..<br />\n聽過佢講佢朋友一直都穿,已經唔跳有幾多個窿..但佢又冇問到下文同解決方法<br />\n(應該唔係好熟既朋友黎)..<br />\n老豆聽日去做手術補返個窿, 想問如果真係好返晒..冇再穿好耐..<br />\n正常運動做唔做得? 舉野游水呀 坐飛機 ETC...<br />\n而家老豆好撚頹又唔知講咩安慰佢.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻眼仲成日有好少既飛蚊係度煩鳩住佢... 我係佢一定好無助..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9cd49f7fff4b032b37ff854bb81c2538e4718e","tid":762754,"uid":126911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推呀"},{"pid":"c36aba481cf50f19623c200d9a59ddc467d180c1","tid":762754,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae3c4f047c3aacfe7d1d55733b68f94ea92a142","tid":762754,"uid":126911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c36aba481cf50f19623c200d9a59ddc467d180c1","tid":762754,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"